metadata.name: Ambient Bloodmoon I
metadata.description:
A classic, tilted lunar eclipse set in a vibrant space themed atmosphere. Glittering stars and solar winds floats throughout the frame, creating a contrast to the omnious red-hued moon.

This piece is first in the "Ambient Bloodmoon" sub-capsule within the "Bloodmoon" collection.

Drawn in Procreate on iPad Pro / 300pdi / 3000x3000pxl / RBG-colors
